pseudo

index page ('/'):
-if no session, login/sign up
-if session, list of surveys they can take, button to create a survey, and logout, link to their surveys

create/edit a survey ('surveys/:id/edit'):
-form that collects title
-field for question
-fields for choices
-another question button (which uses ajax to add new fields to form)
-submit button

login ('/login')

signup ('/signup')

profile ('/users/:id')
-list of surveys
-information

take survey ('surveys/:id/take')

display results ('surveys/:id/results')


